explanation: [0-0] A split-screen shot shows a woman in a red top and black skirt standing in an elevator with a yellow number "1" in the upper left corner. At the bottom of the screen are three cartoon symbols: a cat, a balloon, and a bone. In the lower part of the screen, a blonde woman in a blue dress is leaning fearfully against the back of an elevator, looking at the door with a yellow "2" in the upper left corner. In front of the woman, a white dog is being pulled by a person, baring its teeth fiercely at the woman inside. Below the screen are three cartoon symbols: a baseball, meat, and a cat.

[0-3] The elevator door opens in the upper screen and a yellow dog runs in. A green check mark appears on the bone symbol at the bottom, indicating that the woman has chosen the bone. The woman makes a throwing motion, and the dog in front of her catches the bone, stands up, and walks out of the elevator. In the lower screen, a hand drags the meat into the woman's hand, the woman throws the meat in front of the dog, the dog lowers its head to bite the meat and runs out of the elevator, and the woman shows a happy expression.
